\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日要去拎Report 啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊加油！<br />\n共勉之</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24f7f384c2849be6d145bffa5075cbd1ae11278","tid":454134,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:37:44.000Z","msg":"算啦<br />\n照你咁講 佢根本唔係真心鍾意你<br />\n你無講你都有唔岩<br />\n但既然佢由頭到尾都唔會接受到你同佢朋友一齊過的話<br />\n你地開始就係錯左<br />\n<br />\n情緒病方面<br />\n宜家10個都市人有9個都會有<br />\n有咩講出黎大家傾下"},{"pid":"d0d2e052464e24ad337e8868addcea9a99db58f4","tid":454134,"uid":141669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"早上就抖唔到氣 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b310c733a6179a184ac833d3df6092916c10d3a","tid":454134,"uid":85225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打🤘🏿振作阿<br />\n我琴日同左個男仔表白<br />\n食左檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有病，家族遺傳黎<br />\n我過唔到23歲<br />\n但我依然想用我最後既力量令佢幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日要去拎Report 啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊加油！<br />\n共勉之</blockquote><br />\n絲/巴打 你都加油呀！💪🏻💪🏻<br />\n（原來之前追過你post）<br />\n仲有樓主要活下去唔好做傻事呀！"},{"pid":"91037a8130f9a85698f767f33b1f975e0686436f","tid":454134,"uid":141669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:58:37.000Z","msg":"點解就一定係傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n認輸棄game都唔比咁霸道架咩<br />\n已經係難得有能在自主既事<br />\n我都想抹左以前所有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35f1713b78800f8583a15